cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.CR, cs.SY, cs.MM

The paper discusses coexistence between DSRC and Wi-Fi, which primarily involves network communication and information theory (cs.NI and cs.IT). It also touches upon security concerns (cs.CR) and safety-critical applications (cs.SY) of DSRC. Additionally, the paper proposes a new metric for characterizing network performance, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM) as well.
